Title: Dual billiards, Fagnano orbits and regular polygons
Authors: Serge Troubetzkoy (CPT, Iml, Frumam)
Categories: math.DS
Proxy: ccsd hal-00139790
Journal-ref: The American Mathematical Monthly 116 (2009) 251-260
\\
  We study the notion of Fagnano orbits for dual polygonal billiards. We used
them to characterize regular polygons and we study the iteration of the
developing map.
